high_descs: Turn around and cross the room to face the brown shelves.
Pick up the pan from the shelf.
Cross the room and go left to stand in front of the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the pan up from the sink.
Go left and turn to face the stove and microwave.
Put the pan in the microwave.

Clean the plate and pick it up from the sink after turning off the water
Move to the stove to the left of you
Place the plate in the cabinet above the stove
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned plate in the cabinet above the microwave.

pick up the black and white swirled plate
turn right and walk straight, turn left at the fridge, walk straight and stop at the sink
put the plate in the sink basin, wash it with water, take out the now clean grey plate
